<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ .site_name }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>{{ .site_name }}</h1>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <h2>{{ .message }}</h2>

        <p>
            Your Toutā site is up and running! This is a basic starter template with:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>✅ Cosan Router for routing</li>
            <li>✅ Fíth Renderer for templating</li>
            <li>✅ Basic homepage handler</li>
            <li>✅ Clean project structure</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Next Steps</h3>

        <ol>
            <li>Add more handlers in the <code>handlers/</code> directory</li>
            <li>Create additional templates in <code>views/</code></li>
            <li>Add static assets to <code>static/</code></li>
            <li>Customize your site!</li>
        </ol>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Powered by <strong>Toutā</strong></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
